name: Go Puppy Go
description:
Go Puppy Go!

Help this lost dog find his way back home safely! This dog strayed a bit too far from home and it takes all day to get back. Avoid obstacles such as garbage, grumpy cats, and dead flowers that will distract the dog.  At the end of the day, the dog will need house keys to get back home! Use keyboard arrows to move and press space to jump.

This is a group project with Irene Yang.
